---
title: Sirloin Steak & Rosemary Fries with Goat Cheese & Truffle Mayo
description: Tonight, fries get an upgrade with a sprinkle of rosemary and garlic for the ultimate injection of flavour. Paired with a mild truffle
mayo, tender sirloin steak and lemony sautéed greens, this is restaurant quality cooking in the comfort of your own home.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sirloin-steak-rosemary-fries-3d440e5f.jpg
